00:35:36.080 --> 00:35:37.160
bunch of times today.

00:35:37.160 --> 00:35:39.300
And I'm probably going to
look at my soon list at

00:35:39.300 --> 00:35:41.430
least once every day.

00:35:41.430 --> 00:35:43.210
Beyond that, I mean I know
