00:37:49.730 --> 00:37:51.400
that's responsive.

00:37:51.400 --> 00:37:54.580
Getting back to people in five
minutes, that's unsustainable.

00:37:54.580 --> 00:37:57.090
That's creating an expectation
that they're more

00:37:57.090 --> 00:37:58.980
important than you.

00:37:58.980 --> 00:38:00.950
Our product helps with making
sure that people you do need

00:38:00.950 --> 00:38:02.530
to get back to right
away, you can.

00:38:02.530 --> 00:38:05.990
But generally speaking, most
things don't demand your time

00:38:05.990 --> 00:38:07.360
right right now.

00:38:07.360 --> 00:38:10.440
So anything you can do to set
that expectation I think is a

00:38:10.440 --> 00:38:11.070
good thing.

00:38:11.070 --> 00:38:14.490
And I think moving it to your
task list is a much better

00:38:14.490 --> 00:38:16.050
place than leaving
it in your inbox.

